<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200807/725ee42e58c64efb9874ac2ce0214259.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200807/362bd7a7a62d48ce8ea02d9a5016070f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>